  "remarks": "\nRUSSIAN REGIONAL DEVELOPMENT BANK is an involved person under the Russia (EU Exit) (Sanctions) Regulations 2019 because it is or has been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely the Russian financial services sector.\n",
